chart.description: Number of times a request a connection to a server was retried and/or redispatched to another server
chart.name: Server Retries and Redispatches
chart.programText:
A = data('derive.retries', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy')).publish(label='A')
B = data('derive.redispatched', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy')).publish(label='B')

chart.name: Connection Errors
chart.programText: A = data('derive.error_connection', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy') and (not filter('service_name', 'BACKEND')), rollup='delta').publish(label='A')

chart.programText:
C = data('derive.response_5xx', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy'), rollup='delta').publish(label='C')
B = data('derive.response_4xx', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy'), rollup='delta').publish(label='B')
A = data('derive.response_2xx', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy'), rollup='delta').publish(label='A')
